{"tid":703880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（老中又要輪米）共軍軍營開放日派三萬門票","createTime":"2018-06-16T03:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T13:23:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"96dfe981706c1e1e02010487c0df71c87185b5d6","tid":703880,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"每年解放軍開放日都吸引不少市民參觀。解放軍駐香港部隊將於六月三十日至七月二日，分別開放石崗、新圍及昂船洲軍營予市民參觀。<br />\n<br />\n開放日門票將於本月二十四日上午八時三十分至十二時三十分在中環、九龍東等六個軍營派發合共三萬張門票。市民可憑身份證最多領取四張門票，所有門券先到先得派完即止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/676968/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F676968%2F&d=PrDykcq9WpXi2%2BxGd4XM69tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d7be9459\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F676968%2F&h=dd0dd897\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/676968/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20171020/bc9f92afe2f4456da64d33d1ec72d3ba.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20171020%2Fbc9f92afe2f4456da64d33d1ec72d3ba.jpeg&h=1fef1419&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cb118e159bb6bb9a0af66b6cb0bf61c357b6771","tid":703880,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decf38c9a9364677bb27a53c372231f345a5811c","tid":703880,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ba6336281f4e9deea62b991bb592013f8b9c93b","tid":703880,"uid":36254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97370aec2eccaf4095cb55f1d1bb3